abstract: She said she did not want to “burn down the rest of the party” in order to triumph. And then she lost in New Hampshire.
snippet: She said she did not want to “burn down the rest of the party” in order to triumph. And then she lost in New Hampshire.
lead_paragraph: MANCHESTER, N.H. — It was 24 hours before the biggest contest of her political life. Senator Elizabeth Warren didn’t want to talk about it that way.

abstract: Lawmakers who flipped Republican districts in 2018 worry that a democratic socialist at the top of the ticket could doom their re-election chances.
snippet: Lawmakers who flipped Republican districts in 2018 worry that a democratic socialist at the top of the ticket could doom their re-election chances.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — As Bernie Sanders emerges as the leader in the race for the Democratic presidential nomination, his rise is generating fears among centrist Democrats that the apparent leftward shift of their party could cost them not only a chance to retake the White House, but also their hold on the majority in the House of Representatives and their shot at winning the Senate.

abstract: Lloyd Blankfein, the former Goldman Sachs chief, tweeted an attack on Bernie Sanders after the senator’s New Hampshire primary win.
snippet: Lloyd Blankfein, the former Goldman Sachs chief, tweeted an attack on Bernie Sanders after the senator’s New Hampshire primary win.
lead_paragraph: Bernie Sanders has proposed a wealth tax on the richest Americans, criticized big businesses for turning huge profits while paying little in taxes and said he believed billionaires should not exist.

abstract: Bernie Sanders emerged victorious from New Hampshire’s Democratic primary. Moderate supporters, including prominent business chiefs, are starting to sweat.
